evidence.source_document: Verified Complaint and Ex Parte Application for TRO and PI, Notice of Exparte Application for TRO and PI for Injunctive Relief to Halt Implementation of San Rafael Code 19.50 and SMC 19.20.080(c) on August 16th 2023
evidence.text: Plaintiff Camp Integrity is an unincorporated association of people and their property, and a collectively funded bathroom and handwashing station located at 773 Lincoln Ave, San Rafael. Camp Integrity is represented collectively by Plaintiffs.
